{"tid":1558410,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"係東京獨遊自己過生日 有無巴絲出黎一齊飲野","createTime":"2019-09-10T12:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:07:18.000Z","uid":249690,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54d95005e5db6274259b9b4798588cb88af9bec6","tid":1558410,"uid":249690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"最近香港發生好多野好大壓力，所以生日自己走左去東京過<br />\n啱啱自己食完餐生日飯，依家係park hyatt個間bar坐緊<br />\n原本諗住可以好似迷失東京既主角咁chill係度飲野<br />\n但係依家全場爆哂，得我1個人on99咁坐係度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想請係東京既巴絲一齊飲杯野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a2ee741b65d42f722af4a0760c12dd576ecda8","tid":1558410,"uid":275883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"喂！巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你揾到香港人今晚陪到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論你今日生日又好邊日都好，<br />\n我都祝你開開心心啦<br />\n<br />\n好，一齊飲番杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290212651af43260c090a0c229ded0dee6729a72","tid":1558410,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"Chill n relax 好心情再努力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757d228995aace4529c9a148e030f6eb22065fb1","tid":1558410,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"今日先飛左返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0330dffbdd97cea7966100d5182cd1e7a86514","tid":1558410,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"唯有同你講句, 在日本生日快樂啦!"},{"pid":"ad89a4973d